    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require all pubs and restaurants to close on Christmas Day",
        "additional_details": "We feel hospitality staff miss out on family time enough all year round. We think it seems selfish to have a large meal at a pub on Christmas Day while hospitality staff cook and clean like any other day of the year. We think it is incredibly unfair to them and their families.",
        "background": "We think pubs and restaurant staff/hospitality workers should not be forced to work on Christmas Day.",
